<text><body>
<lb n="0133b02" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0133b03" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0133b04" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1224</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0133b05" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0133002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】歷應三年寫東寺寶菩提院三密藏藏本</note><title>金剛童子持念經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0133b06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0133b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b0701">淨三業真言</p>
<lb n="0133b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b0801" type="dharani">唵&CB02122;弟<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00803;戍<note place="inline">引</note>馱曩<note place="inline">引</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0133b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b0901">二羽蓮花合掌。誦前真言七遍。加持身心三
<lb n="0133b10" ed="T"/>業。妄念諸過悉皆清淨。</p>
<lb n="0133b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b1101">次結普禮一切如來印。右膝著地。二羽左覆
<lb n="0133b12" ed="T"/>右。仰背相著。以二信二惠反相叉安於頂上。
<lb n="0133b13" ed="T"/>口誦彼真言。身住此儀相。心想自身滿於法
<lb n="0133b14" ed="T"/>界。二佛菩薩前有己身。至誠作禮真言。</p>
<lb n="0133b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b1501" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>尾<note place="inline">微次反短聲</note>多<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0133b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b1601">如是以三業齊運。禮觀一切聖眾及曼茶羅
<lb n="0133b17" ed="T"/>本尊像已。即結加趺坐或半加坐。澄定身心。
<lb n="0133b18" ed="T"/>結佛部三昧耶印。二羽芙蓉合掌。開手如掬
<lb n="0133b19" ed="T"/>物勢。以二定輔於二念上節文側。二惠捻二
<lb n="0133b20" ed="T"/>定下第一文即成。即念佛部三昧耶真言。</p>
<lb n="0133b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b2101" type="dharani">唵怛他<note place="inline">去引</note>&CB03004;姤<note place="inline">引</note>&CB03315;婆<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0133b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b2201">以印安於頂上。誦真言三遍。想印如佛形像。
<lb n="0133b23" ed="T"/>次結蓮花部三昧耶印。二羽如前合掌微開。
<lb n="0133b24" ed="T"/>中間二進二念二定六指微曲。頭相去各一
<lb n="0133b25" ed="T"/>寸許。二信二惠各并&CB00594;。如開敷蓮花形。誦真
<lb n="0133b26" ed="T"/>言三遍。舉印安於頂右右耳之上。想如觀自
<lb n="0133b27" ed="T"/>在菩薩。蓮花三昧耶真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0133b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b2801" type="dharani">唵&CB00425;納謨<note place="inline">二合引</note>納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0133b29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133b2901">次結金剛部三昧耶印。如前遍禮印安於心
<pb n="0133c" id="T21.1224.0133c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0133c01" ed="T"/>上。誦真言三遍。舉印安於頂左左耳之上。想
<lb n="0133c02" ed="T"/>如金剛藏菩薩。金剛部三昧耶真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0133c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c0301" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;曰嚧<note place="inline">二合引</note>納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0133c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c0401">以結護身印。二羽右押左。內相叉直&CB00594;。二念
<lb n="0133c05" ed="T"/>頭相柱。二定微曲。於二念背不令相著。如三
<lb n="0133c06" ed="T"/>股杵形。二惠并&CB00594;。掌中押二進二信上即成。
<lb n="0133c07" ed="T"/>本經中或用根本印亦得。今取蘇悉地經中
<lb n="0133c08" ed="T"/>通法真言即不&CB04219;。護身真言。</p>
<lb n="0133c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c0901" type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;訥瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;餉羯囉迦抳矩嚕<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0133c10" ed="T"/>馱囉乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0133c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c1101">由結此印。誦前真言。加持自身五處。先印額
<lb n="0133c12" ed="T"/>次右肩左肩心喉。是為五處。以真言威力加
<lb n="0133c13" ed="T"/>持自身。即成被金剛甲冑。</p>
<lb n="0133c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c1401">次結辟除諸障繫縛毘那夜迦印。二羽十度
<lb n="0133c15" ed="T"/>內相叉以屈二惠入掌。甲相背各捻二念指
<lb n="0133c16" ed="T"/>面。急握拳。心想毘那夜迦。作障難者皆被五
<lb n="0133c17" ed="T"/>繫縛之。辟除真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0133c18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c1801" type="dharani">唵度曩尾度曩怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>娑野戍<note place="inline">引</note>灑野薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0133c19" ed="T"/>尾曩<note place="inline">引</note>野迦<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">引</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>撥<note place="inline">普未反下同此</note>吒<note place="inline">半</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0133c20" ed="T"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0133c21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c2101">次結被金剛甲冑印。即前印以二定直&CB00594;頭
<lb n="0133c22" ed="T"/>相柱。以二惠各捻二定下第一文即成。以
<lb n="0133c23" ed="T"/>印如前加持自身五處。遍身自然被金剛鎧
<lb n="0133c24" ed="T"/>甲光明赫奕。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0133c25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c2501" type="dharani">唵紇哩<note place="inline">二合</note>迦抳野麼娜賀吽<note place="inline">引</note>撥吒<note place="inline">半音</note>娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0133c26" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0133c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c2701">次結金剛牆印。即前甲冑印。開二定頭。相去
<lb n="0133c28" ed="T"/>一寸許。開掌如牆形即成。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0133c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0133c2901" type="dharani">唵紇哩<note place="inline">二合</note>迦抳諾賀諾賀&CB00425;左&CB00425;左吽撥吒
<pb n="0134a" id="T21.1224.0134a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0134a01" ed="T"/><note place="inline">半音</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0134a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134a0201">以印頂上。空中右旋三匝。兼誦真言三遍。以
<lb n="0134a03" ed="T"/>此加持威神力故。周匝四方。隨心遠近結成
<lb n="0134a04" ed="T"/>金剛牆。界界光明照曜。一切諸魔不敢輔
<lb n="0134a05" ed="T"/>近。</p>
<lb n="0134a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134a0601">次結迎請聖尊印。二羽內相叉直&CB00594;。二定頭
<lb n="0134a07" ed="T"/>柱。以二惠向身招之。請尊真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134a0801" type="dharani">唵度&CB00576;婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00344;&CB00680;<note place="inline">武點</note>迦&CB00576;短嚕<note place="inline">二合引</note>馱翳&CB03588;
<lb n="0134a09" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>呬吽<note place="inline">引</note>撥吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0134a10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134a1001">不改此印。便誦後真言。迎請聖尊者眷屬真
<lb n="0134a11" ed="T"/>言。</p>
<lb n="0134a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134a1201" type="dharani">唵娑跛哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>囉麼<note place="inline">鼻音反</note>&CB00085;賀野婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00344;&CB00680;<note place="inline">武敢反</note>
<lb n="0134a13" ed="T"/>迦&CB00576;矩嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>馱三<note place="inline">去</note>麼耶麼努娑麼<note place="inline">二合</note>囉娑
<lb n="0134a14" ed="T"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0134a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134a1501">次結都明王忿怒軍吒利印。辟除諸魔恐隨
<lb n="0134a16" ed="T"/>聖眾潛隱在其中。以明王威神搜棟發遣。作
<lb n="0134a17" ed="T"/>障難者唯留聖者及自眷屬。其印以二信右
<lb n="0134a18" ed="T"/>押左內相交。以二進雙屈並押二信交上。以
<lb n="0134a19" ed="T"/>二念直&CB00594;頭柱。以二定各微曲。於二念背後
<lb n="0134a20" ed="T"/>不相著。如三股金剛杵形。二惠並&CB00594;押二進
<lb n="0134a21" ed="T"/>上即成。隨誦真言。以印空中左旋三匝。辟除
<lb n="0134a22" ed="T"/>姦魔棟擇發遣。便即右旋三匝結成。金剛光
<lb n="0134a23" ed="T"/>明堅固大界。一切凡聖不合越此界故。違越
<lb n="0134a24" ed="T"/>者化三昧耶決定不安。眾聖陰罰違越。眾聖
<lb n="0134a25" ed="T"/>言誓故也。即誦軍吒利真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134a2601" type="dharani">曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline">引</note>野娜莫室戰
<lb n="0134a27" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>緊<note place="inline">奴雅反</note>曳摩賀藥叉細<note place="inline">引</note>曩
<lb n="0134a28" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;多<note place="inline">上</note>曳唵阿密&CB00069;<note place="inline">二合</note>多軍&CB00997;<note place="inline">上</note>里&CB00230;&CB00230;佉
<lb n="0134a29" ed="T"/><note place="inline">去引</note>呬佉<note place="inline">上同</note>呬<note place="inline">聲異反上同</note>底瑟&CB00062;<note place="inline">二合</note>底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<pb n="0134b" id="T21.1224.0134b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0134b01" ed="T"/>滿馱滿馱賀曩賀曩&CB03004;惹&CB03004;惹尾颯普<note place="inline">二合引</note>吒
<lb n="0134b02" ed="T"/>野尾颯普<note place="inline">二合</note>吒野薩&CB00085;尾近曩<note place="inline">二合</note>尾曩<note place="inline">引</note>野
<lb n="0134b03" ed="T"/>迦摩賀&CB00344;&CB00997;<note place="inline">鼻</note>&CB00425;底爾<note place="inline">引</note>尾&CB04132;<note place="inline">多&CB04165;反</note>得迦囉<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0134b04" ed="T"/>野吽撥吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0134b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b0501">便結上方金剛網印。即前牆印。以二惠開散
<lb n="0134b06" ed="T"/>直&CB00594;即成。以印頂上右旋三匝。誦真言三遍
<lb n="0134b07" ed="T"/>即成。金剛網遍覆其上。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b0801" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>半惹囉吽<note place="inline">引</note>撥吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0134b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b0901">次獻閼伽香水浴聖尊印。用前迎請印。以二
<lb n="0134b10" ed="T"/>惠各捻二定根下第一文。以印當心。平舒如
<lb n="0134b11" ed="T"/>羸盃形。舉印當額奉獻。若有香水器。即以此
<lb n="0134b12" ed="T"/>印按之。加持三遍或一遍。然後捧而獻之。真
<lb n="0134b13" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b1401" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;曰嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>娜迦吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0134b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b1501">次結寶山印。以獨股杵印。&CB04238;上節令平如上
<lb n="0134b16" ed="T"/>頂形。以二惠並&CB00594;押掌中諸度上即成。誦寶
<lb n="0134b17" ed="T"/>山真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b1801" type="dharani">唵阿左羅吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0134b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b1901">次獻蓮花座印。即以前閼伽印。二惠頭向外
<lb n="0134b20" ed="T"/>開&CB00594;。相去半寸許。如蓮花形。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b2101" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>尾囉<note place="inline">引</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0134b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b2201">次獻五供養先結塗香印。即前獨股杵印。以
<lb n="0134b23" ed="T"/>二惠微屈。捻二定下第一文。相去一寸許即
<lb n="0134b24" ed="T"/>成。塗香真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b2501" type="dharani">唵迦抳矩嚕<note place="inline">二合引</note>馱<note place="inline">一</note>薩&CB00085;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note>孕
<lb n="0134b26" ed="T"/>迦囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞灑<note place="inline">二合三</note>薩&CB00085;彥&CB04252;<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0134b27" ed="T"/>&CB00576;娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0134b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134b2801">次結獻花印。即前獨股杵印。出右惠即成。誦
<lb n="0134b29" ed="T"/>獻花真言曰。</p>
<pb n="0134c" id="T21.1224.0134c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0134c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c0101" type="dharani">唵迦抳補&CB00612;波<note place="inline">二合</note>母納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0134c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c0201">次結燒香印。即前獨股印。出左惠即成。誦燒
<lb n="0134c03" ed="T"/>香真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c0401" type="dharani">唵迦抳矩嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>馱塢&CB03442;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>能<note place="inline">上聲</note>瑟吒嚕
<lb n="0134c05" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>得羯<note place="inline">二合</note>吒佩<note place="inline">引</note>囉&CB00085;仡哩<note place="inline">二合</note>恨拏<note place="inline">二合</note>仡
<lb n="0134c06" ed="T"/>哩<note place="inline">二合</note>恨拏<note place="inline">二合</note>度<note place="inline">引</note>奔娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0134c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c0701">次結獻食印。準前獨&CB01263;杵印。出二惠及二信
<lb n="0134c08" ed="T"/>頭相柱。餘四度內相叉作拳即成。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c0901" type="dharani">唵迦抳吽<note place="inline">引</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0134c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c1001">次結燈明印。即前獨股杵印。二惠向身並&CB00594;
<lb n="0134c11" ed="T"/>即成。誦燈明真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c1201" type="dharani">唵迦抳&CB00135;波&CB00135;簸野吽<note place="inline">引</note>撥吒<note place="inline">半音</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0134c13" ed="T"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0134c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c1401">次結普供養印。二手合掌。右押左叉交上一
<lb n="0134c15" ed="T"/>節。即是想從此印流出。種種供養。雲海化成
<lb n="0134c16" ed="T"/>七寶宮殿樓閣。衣服飲食上好天樂充滿法
<lb n="0134c17" ed="T"/>界。供養一切聖眾。今略舉一二。若廣說者。一
<lb n="0134c18" ed="T"/>如花嚴經中所說。供養即誦是供真言三遍
<lb n="0134c19" ed="T"/>或七遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0134c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c2001" type="dharani">唵阿<note place="inline">上</note>謨<note place="inline">引</note>伽麼抳&CB00425;納麼<note place="inline">二合</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅&CB00425;
<lb n="0134c21" ed="T"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB02594;多<note place="inline">上</note>耶吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0134c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0134c2201">暨如上諸供養已。以右手輪擲金剛杵。誦本
<lb n="0134c23" ed="T"/>真言。於眾聖前。心想如對至尊。作踏舞之勢。
<lb n="0134c24" ed="T"/>倣像金剛薩埵。於如來前。擲弄其杵。因便加
<lb n="0134c25" ed="T"/>持自身五處。左手執取金剛鈴。於額前三度
<lb n="0134c26" ed="T"/>搖振。表以天樂音聲供養聖眾令其悅喜。亦
<lb n="0134c27" ed="T"/>誦本真言。心住薩埵妙三昧地<note place="inline">此上用鈴杵二真言及印。由來師
<lb n="0134c28" ed="T"/>受密傳不戴於文。凡智有限。或傳之不盡。或領受學者不明置有多種。先後著錯不同。今故書之以草前&CB00877;</note>
<lb n="0134c29" ed="T"/>修行者又慮恐承事供養之中。或有忘誤&CB00520;
<pb n="0135a" id="T21.1224.0135a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0135a01" ed="T"/>遺犯三昧耶禁。或有多生宿業罪障由未消
<lb n="0135a02" ed="T"/>除。誦金剛部百字真言。以補前潛滅除諸
<lb n="0135a03" ed="T"/>過。得身心清淨。與法相應。百字真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0135a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135a0401" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩多&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合一</note>三<note place="inline">去</note>摩野麼<note place="inline">鼻努鼻</note>
<lb n="0135a05" ed="T"/>播<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00256;<note place="inline">勒可反</note>野<note place="inline">二</note>&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩多&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合三</note>怛&CB01511;
<lb n="0135a06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>努<note place="inline">鼻引</note>跛底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合四</note>&CB02852;哩<note place="inline">二合</note>濯<note place="inline">引</note>銘婆<note place="inline">去</note>
<lb n="0135a07" ed="T"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">五</note>素姤<note place="inline">引</note>數<note place="inline">沙句反引</note>銘婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">六</note>阿努<note place="inline">鼻</note>囉訖姤
<lb n="0135a08" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>銘娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">七</note>素布<note place="inline">引</note>數<note place="inline">引准前</note>銘婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">八</note>薩&CB00085;悉
<lb n="0135a09" ed="T"/>地淫<note place="inline">二合</note>銘&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>曳<note place="inline">延結反</note>蹉<note place="inline">倉&CB01239;反九</note>薩&CB00085;羯磨素
<lb n="0135a10" ed="T"/>左銘<note place="inline">十</note>郎多室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>藥矩嚕<note place="inline">十一</note>吽<note place="inline">十二引</note>賀賀
<lb n="0135a11" ed="T"/>賀賀斛<note place="inline">引十三</note>娑&CB00344;&CB00680;<note place="inline">武敢反</note>薩&CB00085;怛他&CB03442;多<note place="inline">十四</note>&CB00085;
<lb n="0135a12" ed="T"/><app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note place="inline">鼻音引</note>&CB02755;<note place="inline">引</note>悶左<note place="inline">十五</note>&CB00085;曰哩<note place="inline">二合引</note>婆
<lb n="0135a13" ed="T"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">十六</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>三<note place="inline">去</note>麼耶薩多&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>惡<note place="inline">引十七&CB01239;各反</note></p>
<lb n="0135a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135a1401">其印二手右押左。外相叉作拳直&CB00594;。二中指
<lb n="0135a15" ed="T"/>相合。此名三昧耶印。由結此印。加身四處。心
<lb n="0135a16" ed="T"/>額喉頂。及誦百字真言。能除無始已來一切
<lb n="0135a17" ed="T"/>重罪。破四重禁五無間業罪謗方等經。如是
<lb n="0135a18" ed="T"/>等罪悉皆消滅。何況誤失小過而不清淨。即
<lb n="0135a19" ed="T"/>結本尊印。二手合掌。以二無名左安前居下。
<lb n="0135a20" ed="T"/>右安後居上。押左名指背交指。於二中指背
<lb n="0135a21" ed="T"/>後。以二頭指各鉤取二名指頭。二中指並&CB00594;
<lb n="0135a22" ed="T"/>合。二大指亦並&CB00594;。捻二中指中節。二小指合
<lb n="0135a23" ed="T"/>&CB00594;即成。誦根本真言。以印加身四處。真言
<lb n="0135a24" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0135a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135a2501" type="dharani">曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二</note>怛<note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">引</note>野曩莫室戰<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0135a26" ed="T"/>拏&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>拏<note place="inline">鼻</note>曳摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>藥叉<note place="inline">二合</note>細
<lb n="0135a27" ed="T"/>曩&CB00425;多<note place="inline">上</note>曳怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">去引</note>唵加抳度&CB00576;吽
<lb n="0135a28" ed="T"/>撥吒<note place="inline">半音</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0135a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135a2901">又結第二根本印。即前最初護身印。是亦名
<pb n="0135b" id="T21.1224.0135b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0135b01" ed="T"/>獨股杵印。此與多羅菩薩印同。第二根本真
<lb n="0135b02" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0135b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b0301" type="dharani">曩謨囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline">引</note>野娜莫室戰<note place="inline">二合</note>拏&CB00085;
<lb n="0135b04" ed="T"/><app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>拏<note place="inline">鼻</note>曳摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>藥叉細<note place="inline">引</note>曩<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;
<lb n="0135b05" ed="T"/>多<note place="inline">上</note>曳<note place="inline">引</note>怛他也<note place="inline">二合</note>他唵度曩尾度曩<note place="inline">引</note>迦抳
<lb n="0135b06" ed="T"/>矩嚕<note place="inline">二合引</note>馱薩&CB00085;演怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>抳吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0135b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b0701">次結頭印。即前獨股杵印。以二大指各鉤二
<lb n="0135b08" ed="T"/>無名指頭。於掌中捻其上節內即成。真言
<lb n="0135b09" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0135b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b1001" type="dharani">唵吽<note place="inline">引</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>麼麼撥吒</p>
<lb n="0135b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b1101">次結頂印。即前獨股杵印。以二大指直&CB00594;相
<lb n="0135b12" ed="T"/>柱即成。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0135b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b1301" type="dharani">唵紇哩<note place="inline">二合一</note>戰拏迦抳<note place="inline">二</note>諾賀&CB00425;左<note place="inline">三</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>撥
<lb n="0135b14" ed="T"/>吒娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0135b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b1501">次結心印。即前根本印。安於心上。以心真言
<lb n="0135b16" ed="T"/>加持一遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0135b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b1701" type="dharani">唵迦&CB00576;吽撥吒</p>
<lb n="0135b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b1801">次捧念珠當心。以隨心真言加持七遍。真言
<lb n="0135b19" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0135b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b2001" type="dharani">唵迦抳度麼<note place="inline">鼻</note>吽撥吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0135b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135b2101">二手當心。持珠念誦身端正坐儼然苦思。心
<lb n="0135b22" ed="T"/>住本尊威德妙觀。即與畫像如鏡照形。不一
<lb n="0135b23" ed="T"/>不異。淨無瑕穢。外想威光。心住慈悲妙觀。
<lb n="0135b24" ed="T"/>愍念六道諸類四生輪迴不息。我今發猛利
<lb n="0135b25" ed="T"/>勇信之心。至誠誦念神妙章句。心住本尊瑜
<lb n="0135b26" ed="T"/>伽觀智。今我身心既得清淨。迴此功德神力
<lb n="0135b27" ed="T"/>加被遍用法界。普濟有情。蒙此加持。皆如我
<lb n="0135b28" ed="T"/>身外。若依本經。更有十五餘道。真言及以印
<lb n="0135b29" ed="T"/>契總合誦習。令便精熟。待至事相應時棟取
<pb n="0135c" id="T21.1224.0135c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0135c01" ed="T"/>用之。以備臨事急難。補其不足。亦非常用具。
<lb n="0135c02" ed="T"/>在大經中說。此不重敘。臨事若要。自撿取用
<lb n="0135c03" ed="T"/>之。</p>
<lb n="0135c04" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><title>大忿怒金剛童子念誦供養儀軌</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0135c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135c0501" type="W">曆應三年七月之比借他筆寫之為令法久
<lb n="0135c06" ed="T"/>住也。</p>
<lb n="0135c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0135c0701" type="W">一交了　　悉地金剛經嚴<note place="inline">五八</note></p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>